<h1>Module</h1>
    <span>Location: /system/module</span>
    <span>The module folder contains all the system modules. Every module is a separate application with own purposes. Most of the system functionality is built in the modules.</span>
    <p class="manual-hint">Modules are located in the system folder. They are taken out of the system folder in this manual only for convenience and to ease the reach of their functions in the development proccess.</p>
    <span>Every module is separate application, which follows the <a class="manual-link" onclick="view('structure');">structure</a> model pattern.</span>